				<div class=3D"feature-summary">
					<h2>
						Features Summary
					</h2>
					<div class=3D"content">
						<h3>Polynomial Root Finder
</h3>=20
<p></p>
<ul>=20
<li>Enter polynomials up to and including order (degree) 10</li>=20
<li>Easy to use POLY MODE screen to set up all options</li>=20
<li>Display roots as fractions or decimals for many roots</li>=20
<li>Choose to display only Real roots for 2nd and 3rd degree polynomials</l=
i>=20
<li>For polynomials of degree 4 and higher, roots display in Complex format=
</li>=20
<li>Store polynomials to Y=3D for graphing and evaluation</li>=20
<li>Verify a root is the zero of the polynomial function by storing roots i=
n Real format.</li>=20
</ul>=20
<br>=20
<h3>Simultaneous Equation Solver
</h3>=20
<p></p>
<ul>=20
<li>Enter systems of equations with up to 10 equations and 10 unknowns</li>=
=20
<li>Easy to use SIMULT MODE screen to set up all options</li>=20
<li>Displays unique solution, infinite solution, and no solution</li>=20
<li>Store coefficient matrix, augmented matrix, and the solution</li>=20
<li>Displays Reduced Row Echelon form</li>=20
</ul>=20
<br>=20
<p></p>
<ul>=20
<li>The Polynomial Root Finder and Simultaneous Equation Solver App is avai=
lable for the TI-83 Plus, TI-83 Plus Silver Edition, TI-84 Plus, and TI-84 =
Plus Silver Edition Graphing Calculators.   The Polynomial Root Finder App =
and the Simultaneous Equation Solver Apps are each available separately for=
 the TI-89, TI-89 Titanium, TI-92 Plus, and Voyage 200 Graphing Calculators=
.</li>=20
</ul>=20
<br>
					</div>
				</div>
